Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.07,0:41:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我们仍要去听歌剧吗?  -是的\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}-Are we going to the opera? -Yes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.19,0:41:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 当然要去\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Sorry. Yes, we are going.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.91,0:41:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,买到票了吗?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}You got tickets?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.91,0:41:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没有 我正要上网查看 一定会买到\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}No, but I will. In fact, I was just about to look here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.74,0:41:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托别买得太后面 否则又看不到\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Please, not the back row. I would like to see it this time.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.13,0:41:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不会\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Nowhere near the back row{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.34,0:41:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次不管多贵也要买前座\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}no matter what the cost.{\r}
