Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.91,0:43:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,*逮捕汉尼拔归案的悬赏金*
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.21,0:43:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,*汉尼拔曾是一位 出色的精神科医生*
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.29,0:43:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,*在1990年逃逸之后 成为搜索的焦点*
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.79,0:43:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,*三百万的赏金将付给 能提供线索使他归案的人*
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.09,0:43:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,*想提供汉尼拔线索的人 请打1-212-555-0118*
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.75,0:43:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,史黛琳 你有没有想过\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Tell me, Clarice, would you want to harm{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.17,0:44:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去伤害那些迫害过你的人?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}those who forced you to consider it, though?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.38,0:44:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你尽管承认\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}It's perfectly okay to admit it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.59,0:44:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为想向敌人挑战\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}It's perfectly au naturel{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.59,0:44:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是人性自然的表现\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}to want to taste the enemy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.36,0:44:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它会使你感到愉快\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}It just feels so good. Tell me, Clarice.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.70,0:44:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么是你童年中 最不快乐的记忆?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}What is your worst memory of childhood?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.15,0:44:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你吓了我一大跳  -需要我帮忙吗?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}-Jesus, Starling! -Can I help you, Mr. Krendler?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.82,0:44:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个人坐在黑暗中干什么?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}What are you doing sitting there in the dark?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.91,0:44:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正想着吃人的问题\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Thinking about cannibalism.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.71,0:44:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,司法部也在思索这个问题 你知道吗?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}People in Justice are thinking too. You know that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.66,0:44:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们在想"她到底想对 汉尼拔采取什么手段"\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}They're thinking, " What exactly is she doing about Lecter?"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.79,0:44:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你对他爱吃人是否感到好奇?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Aren't you curious why he dines on his victims?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.26,0:44:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这话是什么意思?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}What's the point of that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.55,0:44:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是想写小说 还是想捉贼?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Are you writing a book or are you catching a crook?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.63,0:44:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了报复那些侮辱他的人\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}To show his contempt for those who exasperate him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.22,0:44:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以他才偶尔充当刽子手\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Or sometimes to perform a public service.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.18,0:44:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就拿横笛手班哲明为例\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}In the case of the flutist, Benjamin Raspail{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.85,0:45:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由于他供应小牛胰脏 和七百美金一瓶的蒙哈榭白酒\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}he did it to improve the sound of the Baltimore Philharmonic Orchestra{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.18,0:45:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给乐团中那些 没什么天份的横笛手享用\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}serving the not-so-talented flute player's sweetbreads to the board{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.32,0:45:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因而使 巴尔的摩交响乐团的声名大噪\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}with a nice Montrachet at $700 a bottle.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.24,0:45:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇!\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Wow.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.15,0:45:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那顿饭的开胃菜是 产自法国隆特的牡蛎\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}That meal began with green oysters from the Gironde{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.11,0:45:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接着是小牛胰脏 果汁奶冻\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}followed by the sweetbreads, a sorbet{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.50,0:45:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他的你可以看这本美食杂志\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}and then you can read here in Gourmet Cuisine:{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.33,0:45:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"有名的黑且光泽的 蔬菜炖肉 其中材料不明"\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}"A notable dark and glossy ragout, the constituents never determined."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.37,0:45:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直认为他有同性恋\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I always figured him for a queer.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.13,0:45:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会这么想?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Why would you say that, Paul?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.09,0:45:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为他搞的 全是艺术方面的事\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}All this artsy-fartsy stuff.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.05,0:45:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像音乐室 茶会美食之类的 不是我多事...\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Chamber music, tea-party food. Not that I mean anything personal{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.09,0:45:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得你似乎很同情那种人\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}if you've got a lot of sympathy for those people.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.22,0:45:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来这里是想让你明白\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}What I came to impress upon you, Starling{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.06,0:45:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最好乖乖合作\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}is I better see cooperation.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.14,0:45:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这案子不是你一个人的\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}There are no little fiefdoms here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.65,0:45:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你必须随时向我报告进展 懂吗?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I want to be copied on every 302, you understand?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.73,0:45:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好和我合作\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}If you work with me{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.69,0:45:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么你所谓的前途就会无量\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}then your so-called career here might improve.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.24,0:46:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,否则 我不但不在你名字下划线\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}If you don't, then all I have to do{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.49,0:46:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反而把线从你名字中间划过去\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}is draw a line through your name rather than under it{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.99,0:46:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你就前途无亮啦\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}and it's over.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.45,0:46:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想怎么样?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Paul, what is it with you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.96,0:46:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫你回到你太太身边去 难道错了吗?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I told you to go home to your wife. That was wrong?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.17,0:46:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 你少自做多情了\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}What? Don't flatter yourself, Starling.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.42,0:46:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是几百年前的事\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}That was a long time ago.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.18,0:46:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不会记那么久的仇\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Why would I hold that against you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.60,0:46:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加上...\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}And besides...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.76,0:46:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个城里到处都是 种田的乡下女人\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}this town is full of corn pone, country pussy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.07,0:46:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,换句话说...\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}That said...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.94,0:46:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你愿意 我现在就能奉陪\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I wouldn't mind having a go with you right now, if you want to reconsider.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.15,0:46:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我随时在拳击场候教 来场不穿保护衣的对打\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}In the gym, anytime. No pads.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.95,0:46:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会不会是用普通邮件送出的?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Is it possible it went out with the regular mail?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.53,0:46:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会 是我亲手填的快递单\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}No, I overnighted it to you. I filled out the slip myself.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.74,0:46:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且在你委托的第二天就寄了\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}This was the day after your request.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.00,0:46:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我实在想不通\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I did it right away. I don't understand what happened.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.21,0:46:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你现在该收到了\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}You should have it by now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.00,0:47:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没有 能不能请你再寄一份\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I don't. Can you send me another one?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.38,0:47:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没问题 我会特别替你再录一份\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Sure, I'll make another copy especially for you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.05,0:47:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是克莉丝探员吗? 我能叫你克莉丝吗?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Agent Clarice? Is that right? Can I call you Clarice?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.89,0:47:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请叫我史黛琳探员\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Agent Starling.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.35,0:47:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你的帮忙 请问贵姓?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I'd appreciate it. What's your name?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.18,0:47:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫班尼帝\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}My name is Franco Benetti.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.05,0:47:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,班尼帝探员\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Agent Franco Benetti.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.15,0:47:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-非常谢谢你 班尼帝探员  -不客气\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}-Thank you very much, Agent Benetti. -Okay.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.56,0:47:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-那我明天就寄给你  -好的\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}-So I'll send you tomorrow? -All right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.19,0:47:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Bye-bye.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.98,0:47:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是没有线索?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Nothin', huh?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.20,0:47:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有 我还在等 佛罗伦斯和伦敦的录影带\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Nothin' yet. Still waitin' on Florence and London.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.77,0:48:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你所拨的号码已停止使用\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}The number you have dialed is not in service at this time.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.24,0:48:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请检查所拨的号码...\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Please check the number...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.76,0:48:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Yes?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.01,0:48:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有汉尼拔的消息\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I have information about Hannibal Lecter.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.97,0:48:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请问你是否和警方联络过?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Have you shared your information with the police, sir?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.81,0:48:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我鼓励你先这么做\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I'm required to encourage you to do so.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.31,0:48:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在哪种情况下才会付悬赏金\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Is the reward payable under special circumstances?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.70,0:48:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我建议你在采取行动之前\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}May I suggest you contact an attorney{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.20,0:48:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先和律师联络一下\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}before taking any possibly illegal action?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.90,0:48:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在日内瓦有个律师 专精这种案件\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}There's one in Geneva who's excellent in these matters.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.11,0:49:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以给你他的免费电话\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}May I give you his toll-free number?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.21,0:49:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,号码是004123317\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}The number is 004123317.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.37,0:49:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你打电话过来\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Thank you for calling.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.39,0:49:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人向我建议\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Yes. I was just speaking with someone who suggested{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.56,0:49:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,预付金是十万美金\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}There's a $ 100,000 advance.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.86,0:49:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了符合预付金的条件\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}To qualify for the advance{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.94,0:49:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必须先提供目标物的真实指纹\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}a fingerprint must be provided, in situ, on an object.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.11,0:49:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等身份证实无误后\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Once the print has been positively identified{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.61,0:49:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即将余款存入瑞士银行\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}the balance of the money will be placed in escrow{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.29,0:49:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,交由代书保管\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}at Geneve Credit Suisse{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.20,0:49:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以随时检验 只要在24小时前通知即可\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}and may be viewed at any time subject to 24-hour prior notification.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.75,0:49:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听法文请按二\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}To repeat the message in French, press two.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.51,0:49:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,西班牙文请按三 德文...\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}In Spanish, press three. In German...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.28,0:50:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,费尔博士 我是帕齐督察\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Dr. Fell, it's Inspector Pazzi.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.99,0:50:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我看得见你\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Yes, I can see you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.58,0:50:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请上来\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Come on up.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.30,0:50:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,费尔博士?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Dr. Fell?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.06,0:50:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,费尔博士?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Dr. Fell?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.48,0:51:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,费尔博士?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Dr. Fell?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.13,0:51:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照张相\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Snap.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.42,0:51:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我应该嘱咐你多带个人来\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I should have encouraged you to bring someone along.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.96,0:51:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,箱子很重\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}The cases are on the heavy side.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.05,0:51:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许要请你帮忙\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Maybe you could help me with them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.76,0:51:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要搬到楼下就好\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Just down the stairs, I mean.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.26,0:51:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Yeah.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.18,0:51:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这边走\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}This way.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.06,0:51:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在这儿\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Here we are.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.94,0:51:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-那是清单吗?  -是的\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}-Is that the inventory? -Yes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.74,0:51:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我能看吗?  -当然可以\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}-May I see it? -Of course.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.42,0:52:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你应该是帕齐家族之后\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}You are a Pazzi of the Pazzi family, I think.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.84,0:52:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在维琪奥王宫被吊死的 就是你的祖先\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Wasn't it at the Palazzo Vecchio your ancestor was hanged?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.39,0:52:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他叫范斯库帕齐\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Francesco de' Pazzi.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.14,0:52:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脖子上绑着套索 裸体从窗口中被抛出去\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Yes, thrown naked with a noose around his neck from a window.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.85,0:52:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在大主教的身边\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Writhing and kicking alongside the archbishop{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.40,0:52:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,碰撞着冰冷的墙壁 全身扭动挣扎而死\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}against the cold stone wall.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.48,0:52:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前几天 我在图书馆中\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}In fact, I found a very nice rendering of it{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.69,0:52:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了相关的艺术文献\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}here in the library the other day.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.53,0:52:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你喜欢 我可以偷偷给你\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}If you like, perhaps I could sneak it out for you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.61,0:52:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么做的话...\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I would think that might jeopardize your chances{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.45,0:52:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能会影响到你做馆长的机会\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}for permanent appointment to the curatorship.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.54,0:52:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除非你去告密\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Only if you told.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.92,0:52:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他到底犯了什么罪?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Remind me  what was his crime?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.00,0:52:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他被控杀死朱利亚诺梅迪奇\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}He was accused of killing Giuliano de' Medici.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.84,0:52:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不公正吗?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Unjustly?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.22,0:53:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 应该是公正的\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}No, I don't think so.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.05,0:53:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么说来 他是罪有应得\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Then he wasn't just accused. He did it. He was guilty.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.09,0:53:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想就算在五百年后的今天\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I think that would make living in Florence with the name Pazzi{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.48,0:53:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你仍会为 祖先的罪行而感到困扰\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}uncomfortable, even 500 years later.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.81,0:53:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这倒不会\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Not really.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.02,0:53:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实在今天之前\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}In fact, I can't remember the last time{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.57,0:53:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除了你根本就没人提过\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}before today{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.16,0:53:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通常人们 不会把他的想法说出来\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}People don't always tell you what they're thinking.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.83,0:53:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是会确实做到\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}They just see to it you don't{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.16,0:53:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不让你出人头地而已\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}advance in life.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.01,0:53:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 请别介意\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I'm sorry, Commendatore.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.76,0:53:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我常想什么 就说什么\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I too often say what I'm thinking.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.31,0:53:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我马上就回来帮你搬\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I'll be right back to help you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.74,0:54:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你所待的房间 是建造在十五世纪\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}You know, the room you're standing in was built in the 15th century.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.70,0:54:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很美!\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}It's beautiful.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.66,0:54:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的确不错\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Yes, it is.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.54,0:54:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只可惜 我在想...\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Unfortunately, I think...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.83,0:54:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暖气系统 可能也是那时候建造的\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}the heating system was installed about the same time.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.05,0:54:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-那真不幸  -的确\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}-That's a pity. -Yes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.17,0:54:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 咱们把它们拿下去\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Okeydokey. Let's drag these down.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.27,0:54:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这大概和尸体一样重\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Must be as heavy as bodies.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.46,0:55:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-这一套多少钱?  -八千里拉\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}-And the set? -Eight thousand.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.17,0:55:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Okay.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.42,0:55:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 这个要多少钱?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Hey, how much is this?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.46,0:55:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-五万里拉  -我买了\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}-Fifty thousand. -I'll take it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.62,0:55:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干得不错嘛\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Well done.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.42,0:55:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当你要偷他的皮夹时 他就会握住你的手腕\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}When you go for his wallet, he'll catch you by the wrist.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.71,0:55:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,督察 这种事我干过好几次\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I have done this a few times, Inspector.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.88,0:55:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次不一样\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Not like this.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.72,0:56:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果手镯上没有清晰的指纹\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}If there isn't a clean print on the bracelet{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.39,0:56:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么整个夏天 就请你到牢里去乘凉\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}you'll spend the summer in a cell at the Sollicciano.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.93,0:56:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把手镯给我\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Give me the bracelet.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.94,0:56:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先把你的脏手洗干净\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Wash your fucking hands.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.91,0:56:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他来啦\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}He's coming.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.38,0:58:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我弄到指纹了\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I got it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.48,0:58:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他正好握住手镯\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}He grabbed me just right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.52,0:58:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然想攻击我的下体\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Tried to hit me in the balls.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.07,0:58:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惜没成功\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}But he missed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.16,0:58:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来帮你\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Let me help you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.04,0:58:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}No. Don't.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.67,0:59:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,维杰先生 一共有十六处相符\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Sixteen-point match, Mr. Verger.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.93,0:59:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是他没错\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Bingo.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.64,0:59:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,*撒丁尼亚岛*
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.95,1:00:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-是卡罗吗?  -维杰?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}-Carlo? -Mason?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.03,1:00:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都很好\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Well, well, well.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.62,1:00:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-要我去你那儿吗?  -应该快了\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}-Am I coming to see you? -Yes, soon, I hope.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.71,1:00:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过你先把野猪运过来\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}But first I need you to pack off the boys.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.38,1:00:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-现在?  -是的 我知道\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}-Now? -Yes, I know.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.54,1:00:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以为这一天永远不会来 对不对?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}The day you never thought would arrive has.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.47,1:00:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯德会直接把兽医表格\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Now, Cordell will fax the veterinary forms{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.10,1:00:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,传真给动植物防疫检疫局\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}directly to Animal and Plant Health{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.35,1:00:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是你必须拿到 撒丁尼亚岛的兽医检验表\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}but you need to get the vet affidavits from Sardinia.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.98,1:00:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它们如何?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}How are they?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.61,1:00:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,越长越大 非常庞大\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}They are big, Mason, very big.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.16,1:00:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你再说一次  -它们长得很大\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}-Say again? -Yeah, they are big, Mason.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.12,1:00:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概有270公斤\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Really big. Maybe 270 kilos.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.08,1:01:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇!那么大\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Oh, wow.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.67,1:01:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你听到了吗?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Can you hear?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.59,1:01:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听起来很强壮\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}They sound fantastic.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.85,1:01:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Super.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.06,1:02:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在收到活的汉尼拔医生后 余款就会全数付给你\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}The full balance of the money is payable upon receipt of the doctor, alive.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.31,1:02:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你该不会想自己去抓吧\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Of course, you won't have to seize him yourself.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.98,1:02:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要把他指认出来就行\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Rather, just point him out.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.74,1:02:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其余的由我们来处理\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}It's preferable to all concerned if that's the extent of your involvement{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.99,1:02:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样对你会比较好\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}from this point.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.74,1:02:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望能一直参与下去 好确定不出问题\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I prefer to stay involved, make sure things go right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.91,1:02:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那将会由专家来执行\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Professionals will see to that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.87,1:02:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是专家\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I am a professional.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.96,1:04:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,督察 你对这场演出满意吗?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Did you enjoy the performance, Commendatore?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.55,1:04:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很满意\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Very much.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.55,1:05:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾葛莉 这位是费尔博士 卡波尼图书馆的馆长\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Allegra, this is Dr. Fell, curator of the Capponi Library.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.01,1:05:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕齐夫人\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Signora Pazzi.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.43,1:05:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很荣幸见到你\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I'm honored.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.44,1:05:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你来自美国吗?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Are you from America, Doctor?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.44,1:05:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我曾到过美国 但祖籍不是那里\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Not originally. I've travelled there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.15,1:05:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直想去新英格兰\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I've always wanted to visit. New England, especially.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.27,1:05:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那里的食物非常可口\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I've enjoyed many excellent meals there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.28,1:05:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我注意到你对歌词很有兴趣\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I noticed you wrapped up in the libretto.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.91,1:05:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相信你会喜欢这个\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Thought this might amuse you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.95,1:05:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是但丁新生命中的 第一首十四行诗\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Dante's first sonnet from La Vita Nuova.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.96,1:05:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对 它非常美妙\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}It's beautiful.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.13,1:05:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-帕齐 你来看  -我看到了\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}-Rinaldo, look at this. -I can see.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.63,1:05:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"对我来说喜悦的爱是"\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}"Joyous Love seemed to me{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.97,1:05:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"当他手中捧着我的心"\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}the while he held my heart in his hands{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.14,1:05:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"而在他臂弯中"\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}and in his arms{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.97,1:05:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"却是我深爱的女士"\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}my lady lay asleep{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.43,1:05:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"正裹着面纱沉睡着"\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}wrapped in a veil."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.35,1:05:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"然后他唤醒她"\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}"He woke her then{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.69,1:05:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"她颤抖而顺从的 吃下他手中灼热的心"\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}and trembling and obedient, she ate that burning heart out of his hand.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.56,1:05:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"我哽咽的看着他逐渐远去"\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Weeping, I saw him then depart from me."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.52,1:06:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,费尔博士 你相信男人 在第一次和女人相遇后\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Dr. Fell, do you believe a man could become so obsessed with a woman{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.82,1:06:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就会迷上她吗?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}from a single encounter?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.49,1:06:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他因此而寝食难安\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Could he daily feel a stab of hunger for her{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.49,1:06:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有在见到她后才能平静?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}and find nourishment in the very sight of her?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.50,1:06:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I think so.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.79,1:06:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是她会看出他的苦境 而深深为他心痛吗?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}But would she see through the bars of his plight and ache for him?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.29,1:06:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-这是送给你的  -我不能接受\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}-Please keep that. -I couldn't.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.68,1:06:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我坚持\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I insist.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.77,1:06:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Good-bye.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.52,1:06:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我们去吃点东西吧  -好的\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}-Let's get something to eat. -Of course.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.52,1:06:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好主意?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Why not?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.73,1:06:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,*使用者名称 密码*
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.03,1:06:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,*暴戾罪犯的逮捕计划*
