Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.92,1:07:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,医生 这会是你吗?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Is that you, Doctor?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.68,1:08:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请帕齐督察接电话\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I'd like to speak with Chief Inspector Rinaldo Pazzi, please.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.78,1:08:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是美国调查局探员史黛琳\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}This is Agent Clarice Starling from the American FBI.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.07,1:08:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}One moment.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.57,1:08:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕齐\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Pazzi.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.94,1:08:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-美国调查局的电话  -说我不在\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}-FBI. -I'm not here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.95,1:08:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是帕齐督察\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Inspector Pazzi.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.95,1:08:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是调查局的史黛琳探员 你好?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}It's Agent Starling from the FBI. How do you do?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.87,1:08:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在正准备离开\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Actually, I was just leaving for the day.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.59,1:08:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-明天再和你联络 好吗?  -不会耽误很久\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}-Can I call you back tomorrow? -This won't take long.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.80,1:08:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先 谢谢你们寄给我 香水店的防盗录影带\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}First, thank you for sending us the security tape from the perfume store.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.96,1:08:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我指的是 由班尼帝探员寄来的带子\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}When I say "you,"I mean your department  Agent Benetti.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.68,1:08:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在吗?我想和他谈谈\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Is he there? Can I speak with him?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.97,1:08:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-抱歉 他已经走了  -那没关系\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}-I'm sorry. He's gone home. -That's all right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.97,1:08:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实我本就该对你说的\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I should tell you this rather than him anyway.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.32,1:08:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有个重要约会就要迟到了\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I'm late for an important appointment.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.69,1:08:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我所要寻找的人\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}The person I'm looking for, Inspector{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.40,1:09:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就出现在那个录影带里 他的名字是汉尼拔\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}who is indeed shown on that tape, is Hannibal Lecter.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.48,1:09:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Who?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.16,1:09:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,汉尼拔医生 你没听过他吗?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Dr. Hannibal Lecter. You've never heard of him?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.16,1:09:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我不是很清楚  -录影带中显示\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}-I'm not familiar. -And the tape confirms{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.99,1:09:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他曾在佛罗伦斯出现过\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}that he is or was recently in Florence.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.29,1:09:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-是吗?  -督察 他非常危险\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}-Really? -He's a very dangerous man, Inspector.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:16.38,1:09:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经杀害十四个人\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}He's killed 14 people that we know of.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.84,1:09:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我得走了 你是...  -我叫史黛琳\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}-I really have to go, Miss...  -Starling.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.25,1:09:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再给我一分钟\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Just another minute.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.01,1:09:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你确定没听过他吗?  -我确定\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}-You sure you've never heard of him? -No, I haven't.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:27.01,1:09:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就奇怪了\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Because I'm confused.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.01,1:09:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为根据资料显示 你们有人 时常使用电脑\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Someone there has been accessing our private VICAP files on Dr. Lecter{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.51,1:09:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从我们网站的VICAP档案中 存取汉尼拔医生的资料\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}with some regularity on your computer.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.61,1:09:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警局的电脑是公用的\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Everybody uses everybody's computer here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.61,1:09:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许是侦办莫斯楚的警探\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Maybe one of the detectives on II Mostro{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.61,1:09:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上网查看杀人魔的资料\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}was looking at profiles of killers{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.66,1:09:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我所说的是你家里的电脑\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I'm speaking about the computer at your home, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.70,1:09:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是想自己去捉拿他 好拿悬赏金?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}You're trying to catch him yourself, aren't you? For the reward.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.24,1:09:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我必须警告你千万别这么做\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I cannot warn you strongly enough against that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.92,1:09:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当他在曼非斯被监管时 曾杀了三名警员\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}He killed three policemen down in Memphis while in custody{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.88,1:10:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其中之一的脸被他整个撕裂 他也会杀你的\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}tearing the face off one of them, and he will kill you too.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.36,1:10:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我要他尽快离开此地  -相信我\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}-I want him out of Tuscany fast. -Believe me{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.83,1:10:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他很快就会从地球上消失\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}he'll be gone from the face of the earth fast.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.87,1:10:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到棺材里去休息\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Feetfirst.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.27,1:11:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由于他的贪婪 背判了信任他的国王\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Because of his avarice and his betrayal of the emperor's trust{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.89,1:11:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,使得韦格那遭到贬黜 失明和下狱之殃\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Pier della Vigna was disgraced, blinded and imprisoned.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:13.24,1:11:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但丁神曲把他放在地狱篇的 第七层地狱中\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Dante's pilgrim finds Pier della Vigna on the seventh level of the Inferno{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.90,1:11:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像耶稣的叛徒犹大一样 被处以绞刑\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}and, likeJudas Iscariot, he died by hanging.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.46,1:11:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由此我们看出是贪婪\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}SoJudas and Pier della Vigna are linked in Dante{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.37,1:11:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,使但丁把他们俩连系起来\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}by the avarice he saw in them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.79,1:11:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事实上 在中世纪时 贪婪和绞刑常连为一体\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}In fact, avarice and hanging are linked in the medieval mind.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.22,1:11:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最早的文献可见于西元400年 被刻在高卢的象牙盒上\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}This is the earliest known depiction of the Crucifixion{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.67,1:11:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,记录着有关耶稣被钉死在 十字架上的故事\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}carved on an ivory box in Gaul about A.D. 400.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.05,1:11:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其中包括绞杀犹大\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}It includes the death by hanging ofJudas{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.98,1:11:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的脸孔朝上 面对着吊死他的树枝\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}his face upturned to the branch that suspends him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.98,1:11:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个在 班尼文多大教堂门上的也是他\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Here he is again on the doors of the Benevento Cathedral{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.02,1:11:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不同的是 这里的他内脏外溢\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}this time with his bowels falling out.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.03,1:12:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请你听我说 我好不容易才要到你的号码\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}It wasn't easy, but I got this number without tellin'them why{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:04.45,1:12:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-对不起  -没关系 欢迎你来\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}-Sorry. -Not at all. Welcome.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.91,1:12:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-请坐  -谢谢你\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}-Please join us. -Thank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.33,1:12:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这幅是十五世纪地狱篇的画\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}On this plate from the 15th-century edition of the Inferno{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.33,1:12:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们看到韦格那的尸体 挂在流着鲜血的树上\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Pier della Vigna's body hangs from a bleeding tree.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.92,1:12:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想强调他和犹大的相似处\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I will not belabor the obvious parallel with Judas Iscariot{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.92,1:12:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为但丁已经描述得很清楚\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}but Dante Alighieri needed no drawn illustration.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.92,1:12:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他技巧的表现出 韦格那仍在地狱之中\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}It was his genius to make Pier della Vigna, now in hell{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.60,1:12:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,声嘶力竭的喊叫和挣扎\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}speak in strained hisses and coughing sibilants{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.60,1:12:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像他仍被吊着一样\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}as though he is hanging still.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.17,1:13:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,贪婪 绞刑\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Avarice, hanging{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.59,1:13:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自我毁灭\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}self-destruction.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:06.55,1:13:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"绞架"\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}"I make my own home{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.85,1:13:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"就是我的家"\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}be my gallows."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.22,1:13:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天到此为止 谢谢各位的光临\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Thank you, ladies and gentlemen, for your kind attention.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.37,1:13:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我虽然不是学者 但相信你一定能当上馆长\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I'm not a scholar, but I think you've got the job.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.58,1:13:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Thank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.91,1:13:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我能请你去喝杯酒吗?  -这是我的荣幸\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}-May I buy you a drink? -How kind of you. I'd like that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.91,1:13:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等我把东西收好就走\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I'll be a minute gathering my things.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.92,1:13:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢来\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Take your time.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.51,1:13:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾葛莉 我会晚点回家\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Allegra, I'll be home just a little later than I said.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.76,1:14:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和费尔博士去喝杯酒\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I'm taking Dr. Fell out for a drink.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:04.40,1:14:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看到很多人走出来\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I can see the people coming out now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.77,1:14:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好 等会儿见 是我太太\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Yes. Bye, honey. My wife.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.52,1:14:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Of course.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.57,1:14:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才该给他们看这一张\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I should have shown them this one.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.32,1:14:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会忘了 记得我曾对你说过吗?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I can't imagine how I missed it. Remember? I told you about it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.20,1:14:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是我在图书馆里找到的\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}It's a rendering I found in the Capponi Library.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:24.92,1:14:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能看得到吗?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Can you make it out?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.75,1:14:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那里有个名字\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}There's a name there{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:30.58,1:14:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我曾对你提起过\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}the one I told you about.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.69,1:14:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他就是你的祖先\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}It's your ancestor, Commendatore{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:47.90,1:14:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被吊死在这个窗子下面\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}hanging beneath these very windows.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:50.56,1:14:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,范斯库帕齐\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Francesco de' Pazzi.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:53.69,1:14:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另外我想向你坦白\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}On a related subject, I must confess to you{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.36,1:14:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我正在认真的考虑\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I'm giving very serious thought{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.04,1:15:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿你太太当晚餐\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}to eating your wife.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:41.36,1:15:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你能诚实回答我的问题\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}If you tell me what I need to know, Commendatore{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:44.45,1:15:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或许到时会放她一马\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}it might be convenient for me to leave Florence without my meal.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.11,1:15:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我先来问你 然后再做决定 可以吗?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}So I'll ask you the questions, and then we'll see. All right?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.79,1:15:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吗?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Okay?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:04.72,1:16:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}So.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.67,1:16:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你把我出卖给维杰吗?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Now, is it Mason Verger you sold me to?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.31,1:16:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别挣扎\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}No, no.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.93,1:16:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是眨两次眼 不眨一次\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Blink twice for yes, once for no.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.23,1:16:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你把我出卖给维杰吗?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Was it Mason Verger you sold me to?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.40,1:16:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 很好 谢谢你\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Yes, good. Thank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.40,1:16:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的人在外面等我吗?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}And are his men waiting for me outside?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.07,1:16:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是一下吗?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Was that a single blink?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.24,1:16:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你搞混了\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}You're confused.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:32.20,1:16:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别乱搅和 否则我真会把 帕齐夫人的肉片下来吃\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Please don't be confused, because I may have to fillet Signora Pazzi after all.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.50,1:16:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你告诉过警局里的人吗?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Have you told anyone in the questura about me?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.51,1:16:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我也这么想\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}No, I thought not.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:46.09,1:16:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有没有告诉过你太太?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Have you told Allegra?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:51.63,1:16:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 你确定\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}No? Are you sure?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.68,1:16:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I believe you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:59.93,1:17:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 咱们可以开始了\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Okeydokey, here we go.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:08.86,1:17:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Okay.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.69,1:17:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的心抖得真厉害\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Your heart is really palpitating.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.36,1:17:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来不是你的心\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Oh, it's not your heart.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:18.24,1:17:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能回答吗?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Shall I answer it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:22.70,1:17:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经向你的局长说过了\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I've gone above you. I've spoken to your section chief.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:25.46,1:17:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将来你会谢我的 如果恨我 也无所谓\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Someday you'll thank me. Or you won't. I don't care.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.30,1:17:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少你还活着\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}You'll be alive.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:30.71,1:17:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕齐督察?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Inspector Pazzi?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:33.55,1:17:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是史黛琳吗?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Is this Clarice?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:35.92,1:17:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈罗 史黛琳\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Hello, Clarice.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:39.51,1:17:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,消息恐怕不太好\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I'm afraid I have bad news for you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.47,1:17:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-他死了吗?  -你收到我寄给你的信吗?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}-Is he dead? -Did you get my note?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.68,1:17:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望你喜欢那瓶手霜 是我特别替你订制的\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I hope you like the skin cream. I had it specially made for you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.44,1:17:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,汉尼拔医生 他死了吗?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Is he dead, Dr. Lecter?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.44,1:17:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要知道 我最喜欢和你聊天\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I would love nothing more in this world than to be able to chat with you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.65,1:17:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惜现在实在不方便\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Unfortunately, you've caught me at an awkward moment.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.90,1:17:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请原谅我\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Please forgive me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.24,1:18:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}See you around.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:03.24,1:18:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是个老朋友\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}An old friend.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.25,1:18:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 别动\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Okay, hold on.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.54,1:18:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咱们走吧\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Here we go.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:46.32,1:18:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我走后门 必要时杀了他\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I'll go around back! Kill him if you have to!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:53.67,1:18:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢哪样?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}What's it to be?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.71,1:18:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是内脏在里面 还是...\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Bowels in or bowels out{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.96,1:18:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像犹大一样流得满地都是\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}likeJudas?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.04,1:19:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道这又困扰你吗?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Are you confused?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.97,1:19:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就由我来决定吧\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I'll decide for you, if you'll permit me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:18.37,1:20:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Good evening.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:27.02,1:21:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯德\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Cordell{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.64,1:21:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,依你看...\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}to you...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.64,1:21:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的招手是表示再会呢\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}does that look like a wave good-bye{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:36.32,1:21:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是表示哈罗\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}or hello?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.90,1:22:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎么想?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}So, what do you think?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:27.16,1:22:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底汉尼拔是想和她睡觉 杀她还是吃她呢?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Does Lecter want to fuck her or kill her or eat her or what?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:32.33,1:22:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许三者都是\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Probably all three.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:34.99,1:22:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是不知道是什么顺序\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Though I wouldn't want to predict in what order.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:39.21,1:22:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的想法\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Here's what I think.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.88,1:22:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管巴尼加入多少浪漫的情节\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}No matter how Barney might want to romanticize it{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:46.04,1:22:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把他们描述得像美女与野兽一般\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}and make it Beauty and the Beast{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:50.01,1:22:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,依我以前的经验来看\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Lecter's object, as I know from personal experience{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.26,1:22:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,汉尼拔的目的永远是\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}has always been{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:55.55,1:22:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让人逐渐崩溃\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}degradation{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:57.76,1:23:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并且受尽痛苦\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}and suffering.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:00.11,1:23:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把这该死的面具拿走 搞得我不能呼吸\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Get this damn thing off me. I can't breathe in this thing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:07.44,1:23:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他常以良师益友的身份出现\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}He comes in the guise of a mentor{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:10.70,1:23:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像当初他对我和她一样\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}as he did with me and her.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.16,1:23:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,痛苦会使他兴奋\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}But it's distress that excites him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.20,1:23:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了要引出他来\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}To draw him{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.46,1:23:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就必须要让她痛苦\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}she needs to be distressed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:26.67,1:23:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为 当他看到她痛苦时就会现身\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}To make her attractive to him, let him see her distressed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:33.18,1:23:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要他在看到她的痛苦后\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Let the damage he sees{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:35.84,1:23:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而忍不住去伤害她\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}suggest the damage he could do.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:48.19,1:23:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像狐狸听到兔子悲鸣时 会跑过去吃掉它\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}When the fox hears the rabbit scream, he comes a-runnin'.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:53.74,1:23:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而不会去帮助它\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}But not to help.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:55.82,1:23:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我不懂\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I don't understand.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.82,1:23:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保罗 你不需要懂\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}There's nothing to understand, Paul.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.03,1:24:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要知道你能拿不少钱就行了\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}All you have to understand is what it's worth to you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:03.96,1:24:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是 我不懂 以她诚实的个性\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}No, no, I don't understand why she didn't turn this over.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.96,1:24:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她应该会把它交出来的\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I mean, she's such a straight arrow.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:09.00,1:24:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她没交出来 是因为没收到\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}She didn't turn it over because she didn't receive it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:12.46,1:24:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她没收到 是因为没寄给她\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}She didn't receive it because it was never sent.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:14.59,1:24:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没寄给她 是因为汉尼拔没写\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}It was never sent because Lecter didn't write it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:17.09,1:24:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他没写 是因为那是我写的\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}He didn't write it because I did.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:24.98,1:24:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你认为如何?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}So, what do you think?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:26.98,1:24:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得你最好别再帮她\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}You'd have been better off if you'd never got her out of trouble.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:30.48,1:24:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你管得也太多了 我是问你要多少钱?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Oh, woulda, shoulda, coulda. I meant, what do you think about the money?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.57,1:24:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Five.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:36.82,1:24:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我们为这个五干一杯\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Let's just toss it off, like "five."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:41.32,1:24:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你最好说清楚到底要多少\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Let's say it with the respect it deserves.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:44.36,1:24:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是说五十万\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Five hundred thousand dollars.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:47.41,1:24:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好 不多嘛\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}That's better, but not much.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:49.37,1:24:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-能成功吗?  -绝对可以\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}-Now, will it work? -It'll work.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:51.87,1:24:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惜不会很好看\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}It won't be pretty.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:54.08,1:24:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那没关系\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}What ever is?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:59.55,1:25:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白痴\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Cocksucker.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:01.80,1:25:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我从没见过这东西\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Never seen this before in my life.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.84,1:25:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那为什么会在地下室 你的办公室里找到呢?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Then how do you account for its being found in your office, your basement?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.31,1:25:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要我怎么回答\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}How do you want me to answer that, Mr. Krendler?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:12.31,1:25:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我根本没必要把它藏起来\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}What possible reason might I have to withhold it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.31,1:25:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或许是因为它的内容\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Perhaps because of the nature of its content.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.65,1:25:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,念起来倒像封情书\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Reads to me like a love letter.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.69,1:25:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-有没有查过指纹  -没有指纹\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}-Has it been tested for prints? -No prints on it. None on the last one.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.86,1:25:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笔迹分析呢?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Handwriting analysis?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.24,1:25:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"你有没有想过 为什么 那些庸俗的人无法了解你"\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}"Did you ever think, Clarice, why the philistines don't understand you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:30.54,1:25:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"因为你就是参孙之谜"\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}It's because you're the answer to Samson's riddle.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:32.91,1:25:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"你是狮子里的蜜糖"\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}You are the honey in the lion."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.08,1:25:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很像他\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Sounds like him to me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:36.66,1:25:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是说像同性恋? 我说像那个迷恋你的傻瓜\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}-Do you mean, like a homosexual? -Like a nut with a crush.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:41.05,1:25:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,执政官诺门 我想说点...\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Director Noonan, I need to say something...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:42.46,1:25:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,史黛琳探员 我命令你暂时停职\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Agent Starling, I am placing you on administrative leave{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:45.05,1:25:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直到文件的分析 证明我们做出错误的决定为止\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}till document analysis tells me unequivocally a mistake's been made.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:49.30,1:25:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在此期间 你仍能享用医疗保险\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}In the meantime, you remain eligible for insurance and medical benefits.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:52.60,1:25:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把你的武器 和证件交给柏塞探员\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Surrender your weapons and your identification to Agent Pearsall.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.61,1:26:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有权力表达自己的想法\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I want to say something. I think I'm entitled.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:11.45,1:26:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请讲\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Go ahead.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:13.29,1:26:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我认为 维杰先生为了私人恩怨\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I think Mr. Mason Verger is trying to capture Dr. Lecter{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:16.83,1:26:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要捉住汉尼拔医师\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}for the purposes of personal revenge.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:18.91,1:26:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我认为保罗先生和他勾结\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I think Mr. Krendler is in collusion with him{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:21.49,1:26:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,利用调查局的资源 去帮助维杰先生\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}and wants the FBI's efforts against Dr. Lecter to work for Mr. Verger.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:24.50,1:26:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我更认为保罗先生已被人收买\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I think Mr. Krendler is being paid to do this.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.46,1:26:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-好在你今天没有发誓  -少吓我 你去发誓呀!\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}-Lucky you're not sworn here today. -Swear me! You swear too!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:31.25,1:26:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,史黛琳 如果证据不足\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Clarice, if the evidence is lacking{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:34.10,1:26:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就能立即复职\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}you'll be entitled to full reinstatement without prejudice{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:36.81,1:26:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是你若采取不合作的态度\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}if you don't do or say anything in the meantime{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:41.31,1:26:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就没希望了\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}that would make that impossible.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:44.02,1:26:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,史黛琳探员在调查局任职十年\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Relieved of field duty pending an internal investigation{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:47.44,1:26:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如今却被解除职务 等待内部调查\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Special Agent Clarice Starling, a ten-year veteran on the Bureau{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:50.48,1:26:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的事业始于\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}began her career with an assignment{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:52.61,1:26:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,与致命狂人汉尼拔的会晤\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}to interview lethal madman Hannibal Lecter.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.78,1:26:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早先 我们听到 司法部发言人保罗的评论\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Earlier, we heard comments from Justice Department spokesman Paul Krendler.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:59.74,1:27:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请你评论一下...\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Can you comment on the Justice Department's...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:01.49,1:27:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今早司法部所做的决定\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}decision this morning?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:03.16,1:27:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,调查局和司法部 都非常小心的处理此事\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}The FBI and theJustice Department are looking very carefully into the charges.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:07.25,1:27:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且态度非常认真\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}And, yes, they are extremely serious.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:09.67,1:27:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想加点自己的想法\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I'd like to add a personal note, though.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:11.25,1:27:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-史黛琳是我们最好的探员之一  -不 你留下来\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}-Starling's one of our best agents. -No, no, no, stay.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:15.97,1:27:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不相信这些控诉会成立\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I would be very surprised if these accusations turn out to be true.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:20.05,1:27:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道司法部和调查局 真的采取同一步调吗?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Is theJustice Department and FBI united in this decision?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:23.60,1:27:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在还太早替她做结论\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}It's much too soon to condemn her{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:04.97,1:28:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,*佛利逊通讯*
Dialogue: 0,1:28:11.56,1:28:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乖狗\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Good boy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:55.46,1:30:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得她很好\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I think she's nice.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:57.92,1:31:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她对我一直很好 很有礼貌\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}She's always been nice to me. Polite.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:00.89,1:31:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道你不同意\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Don't you think?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:02.47,1:31:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴尼 你知道鹞鸽是什么吗?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Do you know what a roller pigeon is, Barney?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:05.47,1:31:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鹞鸽喜欢飞得很高很快\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Roller pigeons climb high and fast{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:07.89,1:31:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后翻着筋斗快速冲向地面\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}then roll over and fall just as fast towards the Earth.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:11.07,1:31:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鹞鸽又分成肤浅和深沉两种\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}There are shallow rollers and there are deep rollers{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:14.48,1:31:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是当两个深沉的鹞鸽结合时\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}but you can't breed two deep rollers, or their young, their offspring{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:17.98,1:31:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它们的后代 往往会俯冲撞地而死\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}will roll all the way down, hit and die.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:21.48,1:31:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,史黛琳探员是只深沉的鹞鸽\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Agent Starling is a deep roller.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:25.58,1:31:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只希望她父母中 有一个是肤浅的鹞鸽\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Let's hope one of her parents was not.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:58.75,1:33:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,史黛琳 电话的电池快用完了\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}The power in that battery is low, Clarice.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:01.25,1:33:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了不吵醒你 我没换\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I would've changed it, but I didn't want to wake you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:04.04,1:33:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以用充电器里的电池 但愿现在已经充好电了\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Use the one in the charger. Hopefully, the light on it is green by now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:08.46,1:33:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为这通电话会很长 而我又不愿意中途被切断\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Because this is gonna be a long call and I can't let you off{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.26,1:33:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更因为 他们虽然剥夺了你的职责\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}because even though you've been stripped of your duties{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:13.76,1:33:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你一定会继续调查下去 绝不放弃\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I know you won't abandon them  you'll try to put on a trace.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:17.13,1:33:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们先挂断电话 好让你换电池\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}So we'll disconnect long enough for you to exchange the battery in the phone for the one in the charger.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:22.94,1:33:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三秒钟够吗?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Shall we say, three seconds?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:26.02,1:33:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-准备好了吗?  -好了\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}-Are you ready? -Yes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.64,1:33:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开始\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Go.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:34.15,1:33:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-很好  -谢谢你\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}-Very good. -Thank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:36.11,1:33:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在哥伦比亚区 被抓到无照带枪\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Remember, Clarice, if you get caught with a concealed, unlicensed firearm{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:39.11,1:33:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惩罚相当严重\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}in the District of Columbia, the penalty is very stiff.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:42.04,1:33:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过如果你坚持那就带吧 现在到车里去\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}But bring the guns if you have to. Now get in your car.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:22.61,1:34:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我之所以这么做\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}The reason we're doing it like this, Clarice{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:24.95,1:34:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是因为当我们谈话时 我希望你是清醒的\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}is because I like to watch you as we speak, with your eyes open.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:30.20,1:34:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别紧张 那不会使我兴奋 只会让我高兴而已\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}No, it does not excite me. It pleases me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:33.91,1:34:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的脚形很美\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}You have very shapely feet.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:39.51,1:34:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你现在在哪里?把街名念出来\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Where are we now? Call it out.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:42.17,1:34:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻萨诸塞街\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Massachusetts Avenue.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:44.05,1:34:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到麻萨诸塞街去\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Take it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:46.02,1:34:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们就拿你的感受做开场吧\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I thought, to begin with, you might tell me how you're feeling.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:49.89,1:34:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那方面的?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}About what?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:50.93,1:34:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,例如你雇主如何对待你\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}The masters you serve and how they've treated you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:53.89,1:34:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有你的职业\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Your career, such as it is.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:56.69,1:34:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚至你的生命\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Your life, Clarice.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:58.65,1:35:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以为会谈你的事\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I thought we might talk about yours.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:00.69,1:35:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-下面的横街叫什么?  -国会街\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}-What's the next cross street? -Capitol Street.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:03.78,1:35:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在第二条街左转 把车停到火车站去\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}In two blocks, make a left into Union Station. Park.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:09.33,1:35:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的生命?那有什么好谈\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}My life? What is there to say about mine?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:11.83,1:35:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已冬眠了一段日子\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I have been in a state of hibernation for some time{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:14.99,1:35:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乏善可陈\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}a little inactive.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:17.16,1:35:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是现在我回来了 既快乐又健康\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}But now I'm back home and I'm very happy and very healthy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:22.34,1:35:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-倒是你让我很操心  -我很好\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}-You. It's you I'm worried about. -I'm fine.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:26.80,1:35:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 你一点也不好\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}No, you're certainly not fine, Clarice.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.68,1:35:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你把自己奉献给调查局\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}You fell in love with the Bureau, the institution{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:32.47,1:35:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然而在付出一切之后\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}only to discover, after giving it everything you've got{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:35.93,1:35:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,却发现他们并不喜欢你\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}that it does not love you back{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:38.10,1:35:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这点让你愤愤不平\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}that, in fact, it resents you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:40.19,1:35:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比放弃丈夫和孩子还要愤怒\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}It resents you more than the husband and children you gave up to it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:43.23,1:35:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?为什么你会这么愤怒\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Why is that, do you think? Why are you so resented?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:47.77,1:35:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你告诉我  -我告诉你?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}-Tell me. -Tell you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:50.33,1:35:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上帝会保祐你\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}God bless you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:52.03,1:35:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你难道还看不出来\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Well, isn't it clear?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:55.66,1:35:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你听命行事\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}You serve the idea of order, Clarice.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:59.16,1:36:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们不是\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}They don't.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:00.63,1:36:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你遵守宣誓 他们不是\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}You believe in the oath you took. They don't.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:04.29,1:36:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得保护弱小是你的责任 他们不是\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}You feel it is your duty to protect the sheep. They don't.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:08.75,1:36:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为你的不同 所以他们不喜欢你\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}They don't like you because you're not like them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:10.96,1:36:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们对你又妒又恨\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}They hate you and envy you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:13.26,1:36:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们懦弱 任性 又无法无天\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}They are weak, unruly and believe in nothing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:15.60,1:36:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,*快速照相*
Dialogue: 0,1:36:17.10,1:36:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,汉尼拔医生 维杰要杀你\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Mason Verger wants to kill you, Dr. Lecter.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:19.72,1:36:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向我投降 我保证没人会伤害你\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Turn yourself in to me, and I promise no one will hurt you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:22.56,1:36:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你会握着我的手 和我一起待在监狱里吗?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Will you stay with me in my prison cell and hold my hand, Clarice?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:26.19,1:36:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那样一定很有意思\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}We could have some fun.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:28.61,1:36:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你错了 其实我更想杀维杰\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}No, Mason Verger does not want to kill me any more than I want to kill him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:32.15,1:36:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他只想用 不可思议的方法来折磨我\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}He just wants to see me suffer in some unimaginable way.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:36.16,1:36:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是个无可救药的疯子\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}He is rather twisted, you know.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:38.37,1:36:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你见过他吗?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Have you had the pleasure of meeting him?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:39.82,1:36:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,见过\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Yes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:40.91,1:36:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,面对面?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Face-to-face, so to speak?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:43.20,1:36:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Yes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:45.21,1:36:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-他是不是很引人注意?  -汉尼拔医生\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}-Attractive, isn't he? -Dr. Lecter?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:49.71,1:36:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪里?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Where are you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:52.79,1:36:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 再回来谈你\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Okay, back to you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:54.89,1:36:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如今所有你关心的东西 全被他们拿走了\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I want to know what it is you think you will do{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:58.22,1:37:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道你打算怎么办\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}now that everything you've ever cared about has been taken away from you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:00.64,1:37:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I don't know, Dr. Lecter.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:03.14,1:37:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能像你妈妈一样\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Clarice, do you think you'll work as a chambermaid{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:06.06,1:37:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到汽车旅馆里去\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}at a motel on Route 66{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:08.90,1:37:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当打扫女工吗?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}just like your mommy?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:20.86,1:37:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在想什么?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}What are you thinking now?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:23.03,1:37:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卸任的史黛琳探员 你在听我说话吗?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Are you paying attention to me, ex-Special Agent Starling?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:27.92,1:37:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是想找出我的藏身处\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Are you, by any chance, trying to trace my whereabouts?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:35.29,1:37:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-汉尼拔医生 我被跟踪了  -我已经看到他们\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}-I'm being followed, Dr. Lecter. -I know. I've seen them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:38.84,1:37:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你现在真是左右为难\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}And now you're in a real dilemma, aren't you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:41.80,1:37:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明知会引导他们找到我 难道你还要继续找吗?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Do you continue to try to find me, knowing that you are leading them to me?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:45.72,1:37:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是你认为 自己真有能力\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Do you have so much faith in your abilities that you honestly believe{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:49.44,1:37:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能同时逮捕我们双方\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}you can somehow simultaneously arrest me and them?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:53.35,1:37:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过结果可能会和 鲜鱼市场一样糟糕\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}It could get very messy, Clarice, like the fish market.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:59.03,1:38:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-让我来替你做 如何?  -做什么?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}-What if I did it for you? -Did what?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:01.78,1:38:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伤害那些伤害过你的人\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Harmed them, Clarice, the ones who have harmed you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:05.40,1:38:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫他们来求你的原谅\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}What if I made them scream apologies?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:08.78,1:38:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我真不该说\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}No, I shouldn't even say it{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:10.87,1:38:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为若以你的是非标准来衡量\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}because you'll feel, with your perfect grasp of right and wrong{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:14.33,1:38:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕会认为自己也是共犯\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}that you were somehow accompli.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:17.87,1:38:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别帮我\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Don't help me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:20.88,1:38:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然不会 忘了我所说的\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}No, of course not. Forget I said it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:27.84,1:38:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你很接近目标\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Clarice, you were very, very warm.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:30.73,1:38:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常接近\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}You were so close.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:36.93,1:38:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在又偏了\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}And now you're getting colder again.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:39.93,1:38:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对 就是这儿\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Yeah, warmer again.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:42.24,1:38:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 给你的提示已经够多了\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Well, I think I've been generous enough with you and the clues.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:46.49,1:38:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你自己去找吧  -汉尼拔医生\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}-You're on your own now, Clarice. -Dr. Lecter.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:59.25,1:39:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望你喜欢它们 回见\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Hope you like them, Clarice. Ta-ta.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:31.90,1:39:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放进去\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Go.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:50.00,1:39:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别挡住我!\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Get out of the way!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:03.51,1:40:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道歇斯底里人的第一句话是"我没有歇斯底里"\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I know the first thing a hysteric says is, "I am not a hysteric"...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:06.43,1:40:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我很镇静没有歇斯底里\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}but I am not a hysteric. I am calm.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:09.82,1:40:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我再问你一次 先想过再回答\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I'll ask you one time. Think before you answer.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:13.94,1:40:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想想你以前的优良事迹\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Think about every good thing you ever did.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:16.98,1:40:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想想你的宣誓\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Think about what you swore.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.95,1:40:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有两个人在货车里 第三个开车 另一个倒地不起\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Two men in a van, a third driving, another man down.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:22.33,1:40:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们把他放在后面 我想是汉尼拔\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}They put him in the back. I think it was Lecter.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:24.95,1:40:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我给你车牌号码 并且会在 目击者面前再向你报告一次\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I gave you a license, and I'm reporting it to you again in front of witnesses.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:30.38,1:40:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}All right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:33.13,1:40:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我将以绑架来处理\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I'll go with it as a kidnapping.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:35.79,1:40:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会派人和当地警员前往\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I'll send someone with the local authorities...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:37.96,1:40:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望他们 不会要我们出示搜索状\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}if they'll let us on the property without a warrant.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:40.35,1:40:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我也去 你可以指定我为代表  -不行 你不能去\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}-I should go. You could deputize me. -No. You're not going.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:44.76,1:40:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你该回家等我电话\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}You're going home, where you'll wait for me to call...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:47.51,1:40:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如有发现我会马上告诉你\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}and tell you what, if anything, we've found.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:52.52,1:40:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢维杰先生让我们查看 若有打扰的地方请原谅\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Thank Mr. Verger for letting us look around. Sorry if we inconvenienced him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:55.90,1:40:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放心 他随时都欢迎你们\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}He's always happy to see you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:07.57,1:41:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要打电话\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Phone.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:09.70,1:41:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么号码?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}What number, please?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:12.38,1:41:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接卡罗\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Carlo.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:21.54,1:41:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我一杯\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Give me one.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:27.72,1:41:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-他怎么样?  -在睡觉\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}-How is he? -Sleeping.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:30.26,1:41:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把他带回家吧\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Bring him home.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:56.08,1:41:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是史黛琳 请留话\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}You've reached Clarice Starling. Please leave a message.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:59.62,1:42:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,史黛琳 接电话\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Pick up, Starling.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:01.25,1:42:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那里一切正常\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}There was nothing out there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:03.29,1:42:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我再重复一遍\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I'm gonna say it again, in case you didn't hear me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:05.80,1:42:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当你被停职时 就是普通百姓 而不是执法警官\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}You are not a law officer while you're on suspension. You'reJoe Blow.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:10.88,1:42:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了你好 希望你正在洗澡\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Hope for your sake you're in the bathroom.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:53.05,1:42:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巨大的...\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Hylochoerus...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:54.76,1:42:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丛林猪\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}meinertzhageni.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:58.01,1:43:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高中的生物学中曾经提过 你还记得吗?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Ring any bells from high school biology, Doctor?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:03.18,1:43:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不记得了?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}No?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:05.18,1:43:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我把它的特徵告诉你\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Well, I could list its most conspicuous features...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:08.85,1:43:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或许会唤起你的记忆\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}if that would help jog the memory.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:12.36,1:43:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有三对门牙...\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Three pairs of incisors...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:15.36,1:43:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一对延长犬齿\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}one pair of elongated canines...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:21.45,1:43:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三对臼齿...\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}three pairs of molars...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:24.87,1:43:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四对前臼齿...\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}four pairs of premolars...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:27.50,1:43:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上下加起来...\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}upper and lower...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:29.87,1:43:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一共四十四颗牙\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}for a total of 44 teeth.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:39.59,1:43:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它们正餐前的开胃菜\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}The meal will begin with an hors d'oeuvres tartare...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:45.93,1:43:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是生吃人脚\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}your feet.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:48.72,1:43:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主菜当然...是少了一双脚的你\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}The main course...the rest of you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:50.81,1:43:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过得在七个钟头后才开饭\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}won't be served until seven hours later.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:54.57,1:43:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那段时间里...\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}But during that time...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:56.90,1:44:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会为你全身会打满点滴...\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}you'll be able to enjoy the effects of the consumed appetizer...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:01.40,1:44:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好让你能清醒的感觉到 被生吃的痛楚\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}with a full-bodied saline drip.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:06.87,1:44:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我打赌你正在想...\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I guess you wish now...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:10.20,1:44:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当初真该把我喂狗吃\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}you'd fed the rest of me to the dogs.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:14.25,1:44:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会的\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}No, Mason.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:16.88,1:44:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你现在这样\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}No, I much prefer you the way you are.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:20.55,1:44:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么...\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}So...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:23.67,1:44:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚餐就订在八点\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}dinner at 8:00.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:53.45,1:44:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯德 今晚的娱乐活动...\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}You will stay for the evening's entertainment...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:57.17,1:44:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你会参加吧?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}won't you, Cordell?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:59.00,1:45:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不介意...\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}If it's all right with you...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:01.67,1:45:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我宁可不想参加\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I think I'd rather not.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:04.50,1:45:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是宁可不...\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Rather not...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:06.75,1:45:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是宁愿不?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}or will not?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:13.37,1:47:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你弟弟现在的味道 一定和你一样难闻\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Your little brother must smell almost as badly as you do by now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:45.28,1:47:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不准动 手举起来\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Hold it! Hands where I can see 'em!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:52.37,1:47:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Quiet!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:59.30,1:48:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么声音?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}What was that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:01.92,1:48:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯德 快一点\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Cordell, quickly!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:03.26,1:48:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趴下来\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Get on your stomach.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:06.42,1:48:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,史黛琳 晚安\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Good evening, Clarice.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:08.09,1:48:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-像又回到往日一样  -闭嘴\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}-Just like old times. -Shut up.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:12.97,1:48:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你能走吗?  -我会尽力\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}-Can you walk? -I can try.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:18.31,1:48:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看起来不错\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}You look well.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:19.89,1:48:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在给你松绑\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I'm gonna cut you loose.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:22.03,1:48:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别碰我 否则我马上开枪\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}If you touch me, I'll shoot you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:25.32,1:48:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我了解  -不捣蛋你就能活着出去\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}-Understood. -Do right and you'll live through this.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:28.61,1:48:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,语气和新教徒一样 最好快点\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Spoken like a true Protestant. Better hurry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:31.66,1:48:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把刀给我会快一点\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Things might go faster if you hand me the knife.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:34.16,1:48:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第三个人在阁楼上\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}There was a third in the loft.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:36.70,1:48:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 是我后面\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}No, Clarice. Behind me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:18.03,1:49:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯德 杀他 拿起枪 把他杀了\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Cordell, shoot him! Get the gun and shoot him!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:21.83,1:49:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-到围栏里去  -当然！\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}-Go into the pen? -Yes!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:24.33,1:49:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我不要牵扯进去\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}No. I'm staying out of this.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:26.67,1:49:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎样 你已经扯进来了 快去\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}You're involved, is what you are, in all of it. Now do it!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:30.75,1:49:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-不  -你快去！\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}-No. -Yes!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:31.88,1:49:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯德 干脆把他推进去\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Hey, Cordell, why don't you push him in?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:35.04,1:49:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到时推到我头上就行了\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}You can always say it was me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:43.76,1:49:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯德\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Cordell.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:46.90,1:49:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯德?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Cordell?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:48.36,1:49:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯德！\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Cordell!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:50.44,1:49:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯德！\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Cordell!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:23.57,1:51:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉 是我\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Mary, it's me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:25.24,1:51:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我决定提前下班 周末到湖边去住\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I decided to take off early. I'll be at my lake house all weekend.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:28.99,1:51:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别把电话接过去 你听清楚了吗?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I don't want any calls forwarded either. Do you understand?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:31.78,1:51:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管谁都让他们等 懂吗?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Whoever it is, they can all wait. Okay?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:34.62,1:51:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托这是国庆假日呀 谢谢你\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Listen, it's 4th ofJuly, for Christ's sake. Thank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:54.22,1:51:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么搞的?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}What the fuck?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:06.28,1:52:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好 你带酒来了\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Good. You brought the wine.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:30.64,1:53:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一次我手里拿着 点燃的爆竹和朋友打赌\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}One time I bet a friend I could hold a lit firecracker in my hand...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:35.36,1:53:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赌我能拿得比他久\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}longer than he could.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:37.19,1:53:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你猜结果如何?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Can I guess?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:38.40,1:53:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你输了赌注 他丢了手指头 对不对?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}You lost the bet, and he lost a finger. Am I right?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:43.45,1:53:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放心 不会痛的\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}This won't hurt a bit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:52.08,1:53:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有客人要来吗?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Are we expecting guests?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:54:26.62,1:54:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经追踪到电话 警方在十分钟内会到达\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}We've traced your call and units will be there in about ten minutes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:54:31.12,1:54:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你能到屋外去最好\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}If you can do it safely, just get out of the house.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:54:34.45,1:54:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,否则就继续和我通话\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Otherwise, stay on the phone with me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:54:37.79,1:54:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Ma'am?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:54:39.29,1:54:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐 你仍在线上吗?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Are you there? Ma'am?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:54:58.40,1:55:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你必须让客人觉得温暖\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}You need to make sure they feel welcome.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:05.81,1:55:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-那是冬葱吗?  -还有续随子香料\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}-Are those shallots? -And caper berries.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:12.49,1:55:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奶油闻起来好香\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}That butter smells wonderful.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:15.78,1:55:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保罗 你饿了吗?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}You feeling hungry, Paul?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:18.07,1:55:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好饿\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Very.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:25.25,1:55:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主菜是什么?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}What's the main course?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:27.71,1:55:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不该问 那样就没有惊喜了\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}You should never ask. It spoils the surprise.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:31.34,1:55:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,史黛琳 你起来干什么? 你应该休息 快回床上去\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Clarice, what are you doing up? You should be resting. Get back to bed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:36.26,1:55:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我饿了\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I'm hungry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:40.85,1:55:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-哈罗 保罗  -保罗 要有礼貌\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}-Hello, Paul. -Paul, don't be rude.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:44.85,1:55:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说"哈罗 史黛琳探员"\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Say, "Hello, Agent Starling."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:47.94,1:55:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈罗 史黛琳探员\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Hello, Agent Starling.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:53.20,1:55:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直想看你吃饭\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I always wanted to watch you eat.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:55.28,1:56:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你手里拿着什么 是想拿来砸我的头吗?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}What have you got in your hand? Something to bash me on the head with?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:01.20,1:56:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把它放在桌子上\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Put it on the table.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:03.79,1:56:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乖孩子\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Good girl.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:05.21,1:56:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 那是我的\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Hey. That's mine.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:07.54,1:56:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐下来\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Now sit down.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:11.54,1:56:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,史黛琳 我喜欢你的衣服\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Hey, Clarice, love the dress.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:14.55,1:56:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很漂亮\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}It's beautiful.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:16.72,1:56:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-保罗 你说呢?  -好\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}-What do you think, Paul? -Nice.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:20.05,1:56:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Nice.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:30.06,1:56:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保罗 由你来说饭前祈祷文好吗?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Why don't you say grace, Paul?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:33.56,1:56:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我?  -是的\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}-Me? -Yeah.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:36.07,1:56:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-祈祷文?  -没错\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}-Grace? -Sure.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:38.65,1:56:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Okay.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:40.69,1:56:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把头低下来\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Bow your head.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:44.75,1:56:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天父 感谢你赐给我们食物...\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Father, we thank Thee for Thy blessings...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:47.75,1:56:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及你对他们的慈悲...\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}and dedicate them to Thy mercy...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:49.75,1:56:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们将要接受圣餐...\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}We are about to receive...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:53.00,1:56:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请饶恕我们大家...\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Forgive us all...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:54.75,1:56:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也饶恕史黛琳这种穷白鬼...\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}even white trash like Starling here...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:56.92,1:56:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并让她替我服务 阿门\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}and bring her into my service, amen.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:02.05,1:57:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我必须告诉你 即使是基督的 门徒保罗 说得也没你好\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I have to tell you, Paul, even the Apostle Paul couldn't have done better.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:06.43,1:57:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他也讨厌女人\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}He hated women too.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:08.60,1:57:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我能喝点酒吗?  -恐怕不好\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}-May I have some wine, please? -I don't think that's a good idea.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:12.14,1:57:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你身上还有吗啡\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Not with the morphine.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:13.89,1:57:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你最好喝点汤\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I think you should eat some broth. Okay?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:16.43,1:57:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,顺便告诉你 祈祷文里有你的工作机会\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}By the way, that was a job offering I worked into the blessing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:21.53,1:57:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我想进军众议院\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I'm going to Congress, you know.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:23.61,1:57:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Are you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:25.40,1:57:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到我的竞选总部来\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Come around campaign headquarters.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:28.29,1:57:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以做办公小姐 你会打字和存档吗?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}You could be an office girl. Can you type and file?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:31.87,1:57:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会速记吗?把这个记下来\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Can you take dictation? Take this down.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:35.66,1:57:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,华盛顿充满了种田的乡下女人\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Washington is full of corn pone, country pussy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:42.46,1:57:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经记下来 你早先说过了\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I took it down. You said it already.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:45.30,1:57:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保罗 你变得很无礼 我讨厌无礼的家伙\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Paul, now you're being rude, and I hate rude people.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:48.67,1:57:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乖孩子 先喝汤 来 吸一口\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Drink your broth like a good boy. Come on. Sip.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:53.60,1:57:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Good.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:58.39,1:58:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老兄呀 实在不好喝\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}It's not very good, buddy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:58:01.07,1:58:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我加了点其他作料 可能和茴香的香味不调合\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I admit I added something to yours. Perhaps it's clashing with the cumin.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:58:04.11,1:58:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是保证你会爱死下道菜\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}But I assure you, the next course is to die for.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:58:19.53,1:58:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别这样\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Come on, Clarice.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:58:21.59,1:58:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这才乖\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}That's a good girl.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:58:23.75,1:58:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Good.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:58:56.62,1:58:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,汉尼拔医生\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Dr. Lecter.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:58:57.78,1:59:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不用担心 其实脑本身没有痛楚感\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}You see, the brain itself feels no pain, Clarice, if that concerns you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:59:01.95,1:59:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,例如这是前头叶 就算保罗少了它也没有关系\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}For example, Paul won't miss this little piece here...part of the prefrontal lobe.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:59:07.79,1:59:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为据说 它能使人有良好的态度\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}which they say is the seat of good manners.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:59:10.96,1:59:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的档案在边界警局中 有五个重点\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Your profile at the border stations has five features.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:59:14.76,1:59:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我和你交换  -交换?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}-I'll trade you. -Trade?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:59:16.72,1:59:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-放了他 我就告诉你那些资料  -你对交换两个字有什么感觉\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}-Stop, and I'll tell you what they are. -How does that word taste to you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:59:21.39,1:59:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又冷又硬 就像在啜一枚油腻的硬币似的\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Cheap and metallic, like sucking on a greasy coin?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:59:25.52,1:59:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-谁是克莉丝?  -就是史黛琳探员\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}-Who's Clarice? -Agent Starling, Paul.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:59:27.56,1:59:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你跟不上就别打岔\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}If you can't keep up with the conversation, try not to join in at all.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:59:31.10,1:59:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保罗 我就是史黛琳\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Paul, I'm Starling.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:59:33.27,1:59:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看...\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}See...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:59:35.27,1:59:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在这里...\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}here...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:59:37.28,1:59:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脑子就在这个液囊之中\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}right here's the sac that contains the brain.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:59:43.49,1:59:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的需要喝点酒\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I would really like some wine.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:59:49.50,1:59:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-很好闻  -没错\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}-That smells great. -Yes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:59:52.00,1:59:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 要试一小块吗?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}There. Like to try a little piece?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:59:55.21,1:59:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是真的要喝点酒\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I would really like some wine...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:59:59.80,2:00:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}It is good.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:00:02.63,2:00:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 不过只能喝一点\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}All right. Just a little.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:00:07.80,2:00:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喝吧\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Okay?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:00:26.20,2:00:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要有机会 你连我的命都会要 对不对?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Given the chance, you would deny me my life, wouldn't you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:00:30.37,2:00:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是你的命\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Not your life.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:00:32.16,2:00:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是自由罗 你要把我的自由拿走\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}My freedom, just that. You'd take that from me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:00:35.33,2:00:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算你这么做 他们会要你回去吗?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}And if you did, would they have you back, do you think?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:00:38.79,2:00:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是说调查局?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}The FBI?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:00:41.42,2:00:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你蔑视的人同样也轻视你?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Those people you despise almost as much as they despise you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:00:44.97,2:00:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想他们会给你奖章吗?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Will they give you a medal, Clarice, do you think?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:00:48.22,2:00:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后你把它装框挂在墙上...\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Would you have it professionally framed and hang it on your wall to look at...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:00:51.64,2:00:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每天看着它 提醒自己 有多勇敢和清廉吗?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}and remind you of your courage and incorruptibility?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:00:58.64,2:01:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果真如此 一面镜子就够了\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}All you would need for that, Clarice, is a mirror.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:01:03.69,2:01:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伶牙俐齿的人我另有用处 我永远不会再雇用你\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I have plans for that smart mouth. I'm never gonna hire you now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:01:08.74,2:01:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保罗 我告诉过你\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Remember what I said?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:01:15.16,2:01:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果对客人不礼貌\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}If you can't be polite to our guests...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:01:18.08,2:01:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就要到小孩桌去坐\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}you have to sit at the kiddies' table.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:01:21.83,2:01:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,史黛琳 你别起来\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Don't get up, Clarice.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:01:24.17,2:01:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保罗会帮我收拾和煮咖啡\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Paul will help me clear and make the coffee.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:01:29.92,2:01:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你仔细想想我说的话\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Just think about what I said, Clarice.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:01:34.14,2:01:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咖啡\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Coffee.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:02:13.84,2:02:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我绕了半个地球\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I came halfway around the world...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:02:16.38,2:02:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就为了看你如何释放自己\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}to watch you run, Clarice.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:02:21.26,2:02:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,释放我 好吗?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Let me run, huh?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:02:42.41,2:02:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,史黛琳 会不会有一天你对我说...\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Tell me, Clarice, would you ever say to me...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:02:46.91,2:02:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"别这么做"\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}"Stop.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:02:48.53,2:02:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"如果爱我 就别这么做"\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}If you loved me, you'd stop"?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:02:52.29,2:02:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永远不会\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Not in a thousand years.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:02:56.09,2:02:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好个永远不会\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Not in a thousand years.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:03:03.76,2:03:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就欣赏你这点\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}That's my girl.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:03:19.44,2:03:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,史黛琳 我必须承认你不简单\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Now, that's really interesting, Clarice...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:03:23.20,2:03:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我的时间又很紧迫\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}and I'm really pressed for time.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:03:25.28,2:03:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我钥匙在哪里\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}So where's the key?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:03:29.07,2:03:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,钥匙呢?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Where's the key?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:03:36.83,2:03:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Okay.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:03:43.30,2:03:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要切在...\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Above...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:03:44.80,2:03:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手腕的上面...\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}or below the wrist...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:03:46.68,2:03:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是下面?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Clarice?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:03:55.90,2:03:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次绝对会很疼\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}This is really gonna hurt.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:04:47.53,2:04:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把手举起来\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Show me your hands!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:04:50.24,2:04:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说明你的身份\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Identify yourself!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:04:52.86,2:04:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是克莉丝史黛琳\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I'm Clarice Starling!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:04:55.78,2:04:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,调查局探员\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}FBI!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:05:56.84,2:05:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-嗨  -嗨\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}-Hi. -Hi.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:05:58.63,2:06:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}What's that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:06:02.27,2:06:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是鱼子酱\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}That's caviar.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:06:04.43,2:06:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-那些呢?  -无花果\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}-What are those? -These are figs.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:06:07.77,2:06:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个呢?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}And that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:06:12.02,2:06:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个吗?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}This?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:06:15.03,2:06:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想你不会喜欢\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}That I don't think you would like.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:06:17.44,2:06:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-看起来很好吃  -是很好吃\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}-It looks good. -Oh, it is good.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:06:19.82,2:06:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能尝尝吗?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Can I have some?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:06:22.65,2:06:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是个很奇怪的孩子\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}You're a very unusual boy, aren't you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:06:25.45,2:06:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜欢吃他们给我的食物\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I couldn't eat what they gave me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:06:27.29,2:06:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,依我看来那根本不是食物\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Nor should you. It isn't even food as I understand the definition,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:06:30.63,2:06:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才自己带吃的来\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}which is why I always bring my own.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:06:35.17,2:06:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么你想吃哪一种?\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}So, which would you like to try?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:06:42.05,2:06:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想应该没关系吧\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Well, I suppose it's all right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:06:46.14,2:06:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟 你我的妈妈都曾说过这句话\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}After all, as your mother tells you, and my mother certainly told me...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:06:51.10,2:06:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我记得她常说"重要的是..."\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}"It is important," she always used to say...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:06:53.68,2:06:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"要不断尝试不同的东西"\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}"always to try new things."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:06:56.65,2:06:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘴张开\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Open up.{\r}


